{"lastModified":1771253187084,"uri":"c::17951852342::vessel::56722770-37b7-11f0-b94c-2377f1d0765f","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nIntroducing Pandora, a captivating 5-cabin sailing yacht, the Bavaria Cruiser 51, ready to set sail from the enchanting Marina Alimos, Greece.\n\nPandora warmly accommodates up to 10 guests, offering four cozy double cabins and an additional double cabin featuring a bunk bed for extra sleeping space. Rest assured, pillows and blankets are thoughtfully provided to ensure your comfort throughout your voyage.\n\nWith three toilets and one extra shower onboard, Pandora ensures convenience and relaxation at every turn during your sailing experience.\n\nEquipped with, solar panels, bimini, and bow thruster, Pandora seamlessly blends tradition with modern amenities for an enjoyable and smooth sailing experience.\n\nStay comfortable with heating and air conditioning, while the audio system with outside speakers sets the perfect ambiance for your journey.\n\nIn the fully-equipped galley, culinary adventures await with an oven, cooker, sink, and kitchen utensils ready for your use, ensuring that delicious meals are always on the menu.\n\nEmbark on an unforgettable sailing adventure aboard Pandora, where comfort, convenience, and excitement converge against the breathtaking backdrop of the Greek coastline.","blueprint":{"name":"PANDORA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::56722770-37b7-11f0-b94c-2377f1d0765f::assets::599e35e0-37be-11f0-942d-f34e26a6264d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::56722770-37b7-11f0-b94c-2377f1d0765f::assets::596b3f00-37be-11f0-942d-f34e26a6264d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::56722770-37b7-11f0-b94c-2377f1d0765f::assets::599e5cf0-37be-11f0-942d-f34e26a6264d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::56722770-37b7-11f0-b94c-2377f1d0765f::assets::599d4b80-37be-11f0-942d-f34e26a6264d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::56722770-37b7-11f0-